89 Sanidassanattika, Rūpāvacaraduka
Sanidassanattika, Rūpāvacaraduka
140.
334Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ rūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho narūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha…pe…  ārammaṇe tīṇi…pe…  avigate cha.
335Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ narūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nanarūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
